nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Dark Journey (American Foundation for the Blind audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Dark Journey is the unabridged audiobook version of the Star Wars Legends novel of the same name, by author Elaine Cunningham. The audiobook was performed by David Hartley-Margolin and was released by American Foundation for the Blind in 2012.
